        "collocations": [],
        "examples": {
          "standard": [
            {
              "text": "The carpenter selected a sturdy piece of 川竹, known for its strength, to build the frame of the traditional house.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "From the harvested 川竹, they would craft durable fishing rods and intricate baskets for the market.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "He admired the smooth finish of the polished 川竹 flooring, a testament to its quality and the craftsman's skill.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            },
            {
              "text": "Using aged 川竹, the artisan began weaving a delicate screen, perfect for a summer veranda.",
              "citation": {
                "source": "幻辭AI",
                "author": "Gemini",
                "note": "gemini-2.5-flash-lite"
              }
            }
          ],
          "literary": []
        }
      },
      {
